item.title: Best of Banksy, elusive street artist
item.description: The famously anonymous British graffiti artist Banksy says he's on a "residency on the streets of New York." View some of his artwork from over the years.
item.ExtractedText: Graffiti depicting the Twin Towers and attributed to Banksy popped up in New York's Tribeca neighborhood on Tuesday, October 15. The famously anonymous British street artist says he's on a "residency on the streets of New York." Loading weather data ...
